F=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=287.topic&index=2><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Group hunt/exploration idea</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Can we tie to this portal? Not that I really care, but it would be good to know. Maybe we would prefer to leave our best stuff at home. You can count on me for this. And I will be careful not to pull the triger when others are buffing. It's a promise. I won't do it again. I'm sorry. Please forgive me. Sob.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>10/25/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3:23:05 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=287.topic&index=3><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Group hunt/exploration idea</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Great idea! The portals aren't tieable, so leaving our best stuff at home seems like a smart thing to do. If we just bring backup and no-drop stuff, then who cares if we die? It sounds like the portals spawn all over. I've heard of people finding them in the northern mountains, the Lin/Baishi area, near the Crater; just about anywhere in the wilderness.<br>
